OL,5, Samsung has pulled an ad showing a     
OL,6, Muslim mother expressing support for   
OL,7, her drag queen son, after backlash from
OL,8, some parts of the Muslim community.    
OL,10,FSeveral social media users alleged it  
OL,11,Fwas "an attempt to push LGBT ideology".
OL,13,FIn a Facebook post on Wednesday,       
OL,14,FSamsung said it was aware the video    
OL,15,F"may be perceived as insensitive and   
OL,16,Foffensive".                            
OL,18,FSingapore remains largely conservative 
OL,19,Fon LGBTQ issues, even as local groups  
OL,20,Fcall for greater acceptance.           
